{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b8624d70bd","title":"关于注意逃细蒋军配合西藏叛乱在我边境扩大强扰的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"91f8c3da85","index":0,"year":1959,"month":5,"day":4,"articleId":"b8624d70bd"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji41","name":"毛泽东全集第41卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/41-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji41":{"comments":[{"id":"356058b345","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"克诚，即黄克诚，当时任中共中央书记处书记、中央军委秘书长、中国人民解放军总参谋长。"},{"id":"da9c5b45b0","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这份情报说，逃细蒋军总指挥柳元麟今年2月中旬奉命赴台湾，蒋介石等亲自接见，指示他设法策应云南、西藏等地特暴乱，并答应增加对所部的经费和补给，以巩固和扩充实力。柳元麟返缅后积极部署，拟以云南西盟地区为重点，纠集徒，发动暴乱。在这份情报的题目旁边，毛泽东还批有“注意”二字。"}],"contents":[{"id":"d63c8c2efe","type":"title","text":"关于注意逃缅将军配合西藏叛乱在我边境扩大验扰的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd"},{"id":"356058b345","type":"paragraph","text":"克诚啊志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd"},{"id":"da9c5b45b0","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）第三件情报应发给云南省委、军区并转有关地区各级党政军直至基层干部，引起警惕，准备应付可能的变乱；（二）指示云南省委、军区立即加强有关地区的工作，派得力人去各地调查情况，研究对策，千万不可马糊大意，轻易相信下面太平无事的书面报告。军委亦应派员去云南布置对策。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd"},{"id":"c26be6c31f","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd"},{"id":"807ea36dd9","type":"paragraph","text":"五月四日上午五时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd"}],"page":{"id":"2d86d86e77","publicationId":"maoquanji41","articleId":"b8624d70bd","start":497,"end":497}}}},"__N_SSG":true}